---
title: Teriyaki Beef Strips & Mushroom Rice Bowl with Pre-Prepped Veggies & Sesame Dressing
description: Centre yourself and relax with a bowl of teriyaki-flavoured beef strips. The mushrooms really lend an earthy taste that’s too
good to be true. So sit back and enjoy this easy-to-make dinner with no fuss and a lot of flavour.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

